Review Content:
What an amazing stay in this lovely hotel. We had a great time from the moment we arrived and greeted by Ms. Guia in the lobby to the excellent customer service of Ms. Charito Sumayao who took care of us until the day we checked out. We will highly recommend this property to our friends in the Philippines and abroad. Can't wait to stay back to this amazing property. Also, thank you so much to all the staff of Bai cafe who are so friendly and delighfully welcome us with the big breakfast and sumptuous dinner. Overall, we are so happy and overwhelmed.

Truly delighted,
@briadventurez
